# Allowlist approach - exclude everything, then include what we need
# ---------

# Ignore everything by default
**/**

# Ignore parent directories (workspace support)
../**
../../**

# Include essential files
!package.json
!README.**
!CHANGELOG.md
!LICENSE*

# Include compiled bundles (but exclude source maps)
!dist/*.js
!dist/*.LICENSE.txt

# Include resources
!resources/logo/*
!resources/walkthrough/*
!docs/**

# Include Python scripts needed at runtime
!src/scripts/*.py
